about.summary: Computes exact conditional p-values and quantiles using an implementation of the Shift-Algorithm by Streitberg & Roehmel.

name: r-exactranktests
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.8-31" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-exactranktests
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/exactRankTests_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/exactRankTests/exactRankTests_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fca19ef48fb50b9770d24d4b36715b889e6e57d2f8a0dbaa82d28e16d96ca484

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('exactRankTests')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('exactRankTests')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=exactRankTests
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Computes exact conditional p-values and quantiles using an implementation of the Shift-Algorithm
    by Streitberg & Roehmel.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
